---
title: Middle Eastern Chickpea & Roast Veggie Bowl with Freekeh & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Go big or go home! That was our philosophy with the bold flavours in this veggie sensation. There’s chermoula roast veggies, plus spiced chickpeas and a lightly seasoned couscous that's all brought together with a cooling garlic yoghurt. Go big with us, you’ll be glad you did.
